          "Viewed in that light, borrowing against Uniswap LP positions is not just another lending feature. It is a new way of connecting two parts of DeFi that have often remained separate: active market liquidity and usable credit. Aave v4’s architecture provides the right foundation because it allows shared liquidity and specialized collateral logic to coexist cleanly. Avana builds on that foundation by focusing specifically on LP collateral, where valuation, liquidation, and risk treatment all need to be designed around the position itself rather than assumed away.",
